üß© 1. Basic Form with action and method
<form action="submit.html" method="post">
  <label>Username:</label>
  <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Enter your name">

  <label>Password:</label>
  <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Enter your password">

  <input type="submit" value="Login">
</form>


Explanation:

action ‚Üí defines where the data goes.

method ‚Üí GET (adds data to URL) or POST (sends securely).

‚úâÔ∏è 2. target Attribute
<form action="welcome.html" target="_blank">
  <label>Email:</label>
  <input type="email" name="email">
  <input type="submit" value="Open in New Tab">
</form>


Explanation:

target="_blank" ‚Üí opens the result in a new tab.

üìÅ 3. enctype Attribute (for File Uploads)
<form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <label>Upload Image:</label>
  <input type="file" name="photo" accept="image/*">
  <input type="submit" value="Upload">
</form>


Explanation:

enctype="multipart/form-data" ‚Üí required when uploading files.

üß† 4. autocomplete, novalidate
<form action="/login" method="post" autocomplete="on" novalidate>
  <label>Username:</label>
  <input type="text" name="user" autocomplete="username">

  <label>Password:</label>
  <input type="password" name="pass" autocomplete="current-password">

  <input type="submit" value="Login">
</form>


Explanation:

autocomplete="on/off" ‚Üí browser auto-fills data.

novalidate ‚Üí disables HTML5 validation.

üéØ 5. name, value, readonly, disabled
<form>
  <label>Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fullname" value="Devendra">

  <label>City:</label>
  <input type="text" value="Kurnool" readonly>

  <label>PIN Code:</label>
  <input type="text" value="518001" disabled>

  <input type="submit">
</form>


Explanation:

readonly ‚Üí user can‚Äôt change but field is sent.

disabled ‚Üí user can‚Äôt change and field is not sent.

‚öôÔ∏è 6. form Attribute (External Button Control)
<form id="infoForm">
  <label>First Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fname">
</form>

<input type="submit" form="infoForm" value="Submit Form">


Explanation:

The submit button is outside the form but linked using form="infoForm".

üí° 7. All-In-One Example
<form action="/submit" method="post" target="_blank"
      enctype="multipart/form-data" autocomplete="on" novalidate>
  <h3>Registration Form</h3>

  <label>Full Name:</label>
  <input type="text" name="fullname" required>

  <label>Email:</label>
  <input type="email" name="email" required>

  <label>Profile Photo:</label>
  <input type="file" name="photo">

  <input type="submit" value="Register">
</form>


Attributes used: action, method, target, enctype, autocomplete, novalidate, required.


üßæ 1. Form Attributes Example ‚Äì Name / Value Table
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Form Attributes Example</title>
  <style>
    table { border-collapse: collapse; }
    td, th { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h3>Form Attributes Example</h3>
  <form>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Name</th><th>Value</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Name</td>
          <td><input type="text" name="name"></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sex</td>
          <td><input type="radio" name="sex"> Male
              <input type="radio" name="sex"> Female</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Eye color</td>
          <td>
            <select>
              <option>Green</option>
              <option>Brown</option>
              <option>Blue</option>
            </select>
          </td></tr>
      <tr><td>Check all that apply</td>
          <td>
            <input type="checkbox"> Over 6 feet tall <br>
            <input type="checkbox"> Over 200 pounds
          </td></tr>
      <tr><td>Describe your athletic ability</td>
          <td><textarea rows="3" cols="25"></textarea></td></tr>
    </table><br>
    <input type="submit" value="Enter my information">
  </form>
</body>
</html>

üßæ 2. Novell Services Login
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Novell Services Login</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h3>Novell Services Login</h3>
  <form>
    Username: <input type="text"><br><br>
    Password: <input type="password"><br><br>
    City of Employment: <input type="text"><br><br>
    Web server:
    <select>
      <option>Choose a server</option>
      <option>Server 1</option>
      <option>Server 2</option>
    </select><br><br>

    Please specify your role:<br>
    <input type="radio" name="role"> Admin <br>
    <input type="radio" name="role"> Engineer <br>
    <input type="radio" name="role"> Manager <br>
    <input type="radio" name="role"> Guest <br><br>

    Single sign-on to the following:<br>
    <input type="checkbox"> Mail 
    <input type="checkbox"> Payroll 
    <input type="checkbox"> Self-service <br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Login">
    <input type="reset" value="Reset">
  </form>
</body>
</html>

üßæ 3. Simple Event Registration
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Simple Event Registration</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Simple Event Registration</h2>
  <p>Fill out the form to register to our event</p>

  <form>
    <label>Name</label><br>
    <input type="text" placeholder="First Name">
    <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name"><br><br>

    <label>Title</label><br>
    <input type="text"><br><br>

    <label>Company</label><br>
    <input type="text"><br><br>

    <label>E-mail</label><br>
    <input type="email" placeholder="ex: myname@example.com"><br><br>

    <label>Phone Number</label><br>
    (<input type="text" size="3" maxlength="3">) ‚Äì 
    <input type="text" size="7" maxlength="7"><br><br>

    <label>Are you an existing customer?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="existing" value="yes"> Yes 
    <input type="radio" name="existing" value="no"> No <br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Register">
  </form>
</body>
</html>

üßæ 4. Request for White Paper
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Request for White Paper</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Request for White Paper</h2>
  <p>Please fill out the form below. If you have any questions, please e-mail <a href="mailto:whitepaper@tekfrom.com">whitepaper@tekfrom.com</a>.</p>
  <p>* ‚Äì required fields</p>

  <form>
    *First Name: <input type="text" required><br><br>
    *Last Name: <input type="text" required><br><br>
    Company Name: <input type="text"><br><br>
    Company/Personal Website: <input type="url"><br><br>
    *Email: <input type="email" required><br><br>
    Phone: <input type="tel"> Ext: <input type="text" size="4"><br><br>
    State/Province:
    <select>
      <option>Select for USA or Canada only</option>
      <option>California</option>
      <option>Texas</option>
      <option>Ontario</option>
    </select><br><br>
    *Country:
    <select>
      <option>United States</option>
      <option>Canada</option>
      <option>India</option>
    </select><br><br>
    Comments:<br>
    <textarea rows="3" cols="40"></textarea><br><br>
    <input type="submit" value="Request White Paper">
  </form>
</body>
</html>

üßæ 5. User Registration Form Demo (Validated Using JavaScript)
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>User Registration Form Demo</title>
  <script>
    function validateForm() {
      let email = document.getElementById("email").value;
      let reemail = document.getElementById("reemail").value;
      if (email !== reemail) {
        alert("Emails do not match!");
        return false;
      }
      return true;
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>User Registration Form Demo</h2>
  <p>Form Validated Using JavaScript</p>

  <form onsubmit="return validateForm()">
    <input type="text" placeholder="First Name" required>
    <input type="text" placeholder="Last Name" required><br><br>

    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email" required><br><br>
    <input type="email" id="reemail" placeholder="Re-enter Email" required><br><br>

    <input type="password" placeholder="New Password" required><br><br>

    Birthday: 
    <select><option>Month</option></select>
    <select><option>Day</option></select>
    <select><option>Year</option></select><br><br>

    <input type="radio" name="gender"> Female
    <input type="radio" name="gender"> Male<br><br>

    <button type="submit">Sign Up</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
